8.3 Use if_else() for conditional logic


Show the code
mpg |&gt;
  mutate(
    big_engine = if_else(displ &gt;= 4, "Yes", "No")
  ) |&gt;
  count(big_engine)


# A tibble: 2 × 2
  big_engine     n
  &lt;chr&gt;      &lt;int&gt;
1 No           148
2 Yes           86

